{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/dev/knowledge/oop","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6ea259b8-24a2-5958-bcd8-75c4249031c5","html":"<h1 id=\"슈퍼개발자-춤추는망고입니다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8A%88%ED%8D%BC%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EC%9E%90-%EC%B6%A4%EC%B6%94%EB%8A%94%EB%A7%9D%EA%B3%A0%EC%9E%85%EB%8B%88%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"슈퍼개발자 춤추는망고입니다 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>슈퍼개발자, 춤추는망고입니다.</h1>\n<p>( <del>춤 안춥니다.</del> )</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"더-나은-개발방식-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8D%94-%EB%82%98%EC%9D%80-%EA%B0%9C%EB%B0%9C%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D-\" aria-label=\"더 나은 개발방식  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>더 나은 개발방식 !</h2>\n<h1 id=\"객체지향-프로그래밍-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%A7%80%ED%96%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%B0%8D-\" aria-label=\"객체지향 프로그래밍  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>객체지향 프로그래밍 !</h1>\n<p><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"객체지향-프로그래밍이란-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%A7%80%ED%96%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%B0%8D%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80-\" aria-label=\"객체지향 프로그래밍이란  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>객체지향 프로그래밍이란 ?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">프로그래밍에서 필요한 데이터를 추상화시켜,\n\n상태와 행위를 가진 객체를 만들고,\n\n그 객체들 간의 유기적인 상호작용을 통해\n\n로직을 구성하는 프로그래밍 방법</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"즉\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A6%89\" aria-label=\"즉 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>즉,</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">컴퓨터 프로그램을 명령어의 집합으로 보는 것이 아닌,\n\n여러 개의 독립된 단위인 &#39;객체&#39;,\n\n그것들의 모임으로 파악하고자 하는 인식/개발 방식이죠!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">프로그램 설계방법론, 개념 중 하나에요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"왜-객체지향\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%99%9C-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%A7%80%ED%96%A5\" aria-label=\"왜 객체지향 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>왜 객체지향?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">초기 프로그래밍 방식인 &#39;절차지향&#39; 의 문제를 해결하기 위해 등장했어요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">1. 개발, 보수가 간편하다!\n\n2. 더 직관적인 코드분석이 가능하다!\n\n3. 코드를 재사용하기 좋다!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">위와 같은 장점을 통해,\n\n프로그램을 유연하게, 변경이 용이하게 만들기 때문이죠!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"구성요소-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-\" aria-label=\"구성요소  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구성요소 ?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">객체지향에는,\n\n재사용과 구조화 설계를 위해 사용하는\n\n여러 정보 형태가 있는데요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"객체지향-프로그래밍의-구성요소-글에-있어요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%A7%80%ED%96%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%B0%8D%EC%9D%98-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EA%B8%80%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%88%EC%96%B4%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"객체지향 프로그래밍의 구성요소 글에 있어요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/posts/dev/knowledge/oop_component\">객체지향 프로그래밍의 구성요소</a> 글에 있어요!</h3>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"특징은-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95%EC%9D%80-\" aria-label=\"특징은  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징은 ?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">위에서 본 객체지향 프로그래밍의 장점은\n\n여러가지 특징들을 기반으로 하는데요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"객체지향-프로그래밍의-특징-글에-있어요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EC%A7%80%ED%96%A5-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%98%EB%B0%8D%EC%9D%98-%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95-%EA%B8%80%EC%97%90-%EC%9E%88%EC%96%B4%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"객체지향 프로그래밍의 특징 글에 있어요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/posts/dev/knowledge/oop_characteristics\">객체지향 프로그래밍의 특징</a> 글에 있어요!</h3>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"top-down-bottom-up-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#top-down-bottom-up-\" aria-label=\"top down bottom up  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Top-Down? Bottom-Up ?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">객체지향 프로그래밍은\n\n프로그램이라는 큰 문제를 해결하기 위해,\n\n몇개의 작은 문제로 나눠 해결하는 방식이기도 해서,\n\nTop-Down 방식 프로그래밍이라고도 해요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">또,\n\n작은 문제들을 해결하는 객체들을 만든 뒤,\n\n그 객체들을 조합하여 큰 문제를 해결하는 방식이기도 해서,\n\nBottom-Up 방식 프로그래밍이라고도 해요!</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/dev/knowledge/oop","tagSlugs":["/tag/knowledge/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-29","description":"객체지향 프로그래밍에 대한 글입니다.","tags":["knowledge"],"title":"객체지향 프로그래밍 ?","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/dev/knowledge/oop"}}}